üñ§ Dark UI Design System

A premium, minimal, and accessible dark theme system for web and product interfaces. Designed for clarity, softness, and contrast, this guide defines the foundational tokens, components, and styles to enable consistent, branded UI generation.

‚úÖ Optimized for use with design automation tools and AI theming engines

