üÉè Cards

Elevation 1 ‚Äì Static / Grayed
	‚Ä¢	Radius: 34px
	‚Ä¢	BG: neutral850
	‚Ä¢	Border: neutral700
	‚Ä¢	Hover: Dim to 85% (if interactive)

Elevation 2 ‚Äì Interactive
	‚Ä¢	Radius: 15px
	‚Ä¢	BG: neutral800
	‚Ä¢	Border: neutral700
	‚Ä¢	Drop Shadow:
	‚Ä¢	Offset: 12px 12px
	‚Ä¢	Blur: 24px
	‚Ä¢	Color: #000000 @15%
	‚Ä¢	Hover: Dim to 85%

