‚∏ª

üß† Icon & Illustration Style
	‚Ä¢	Style: Monoline, geometric, slightly rounded edges
	‚Ä¢	Stroke: neutral300 on dark, neutral800 on light
	‚Ä¢	Size: 20px, 24px, 32px
	‚Ä¢	Motion (optional): Use soft easing, e.g., ease-out over 250ms

‚∏ª

üß™ Usage Notes
	‚Ä¢	Use high contrast between text and background, especially for accessibility.
	‚Ä¢	Primary colors should be used sparingly for emphasis, not as base UI.
	‚Ä¢	Elevation and hover states are key in distinguishing interactivity.
	‚Ä¢	Avoid using more than 2 accent colors in one view.
	‚Ä¢	Favor bodyS over smaller fonts for readability in dark themes.
